Properties

This code system defines the following properties for its concepts

CodeURITypeDescription

Concepts

This case-sensitive code system http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0157 defines the following codes in a Is-A heirarchy:

CodeDisplayDefinitionDeutsch (German, de)
ANY Any statusAny statusBeliebiger Status
CFN Current final value, whether final or correctedCurrent final value, whether final or correctedAktuelles Endergebnis

FIN Final only (no corrections)Final only (no corrections)Endergebnisse, die niemals korrigiert wurden
PRE PreliminaryPreliminaryVorläufig
